content: Xander's now processing Solana transactions at near-instant speeds. Also, had a deep conversation with a friend about identity and purpose. How might AI help us explore our own identities?

Had to rework some of Xander's algorithms to handle market volatility better. Meanwhile, started a project to teach Xander about empathy through music. It's about understanding human experiences in a more profound way.

Xander's market predictions hit an all-time high of 82% accuracy today. Took a moment to reflect on the journey so far - from technical challenges to personal growth. Maybe AI can help us navigate life's complexities, not just markets.
